      "review_text": "I was really looking forward to this one. Its fun and addicting once you get the controls down. The power ups are really cool and unique as well. One thing id change is the UI cause It's a little elementary. But this is a good quick fun. If i ever get a steam deck i might pick it back up for a quick session every once in a while.",
      "timestamp_created": 1774044058
    },
    {
      "review_id": "221272343",
