      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 6,
      "review_text": "Endless fun wrapped in an asteroids-esque modern arcade game. Can't wait to try out all the ships and get the global high score!",
      "timestamp_created": 1774100641
    },
    {
      "review_id": "221277360",
      "author_steamid": "76561198150574900",
      "voted_up": true,
      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 7,
      "review_text": "Blast from the past. An upgrade of classic retro gaming where power ups and mobility are the foundational mechanics. Chaos galore leads to an itch that you keep needing to scratch. I followed this game through the demo and am impressed with the creative growth that I've witnessed.",
      "timestamp_created": 1774103681
    },
    {
      "review_id": "221283525",
      "author_steamid": "76561198020474727",
      "voted_up": true,
      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 9,
      "review_text": "Honestly a really entertaining twist on an all-time classic. I know asteroids. You know asteroids. You love asteroids. Unless someone's making pong more modern this is about AS classic of a game as you can get and improve upon with modern indie game sensibilities.",
      "timestamp_created": 1774107194
    },
